            </ul>
            <h4>Neighbouring Municipality Rules</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="https://www.oshawa.ca/business-development/housing-permits-and-licences/short-term-rentals/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Oshawa STR Licensing</a></li>
              <li><a href="/blog/oshawa-airbnb-short-term-rental-rules-2026">Our Oshawa STR Guide 2026</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

